ement on dual nationality reached:\n\nChina and Indonesia had reached agreement on the renunciation of Chinese nationality by those Overseas Chinese in Indonesia who wished to adopt Indonesian citizenship. A joint declaration of principles is likely to be issued in the next day or two. The status of Overseas Chinese who do not desire Indonesian citizenship will be dealt with in subsequent negotiations.\n\nComment: China's past insistence on the principle of dual nationality has been a major irritant to Southeast Asian countries, and the abandonment of this principle will be viewed favorably by these countries. Indonesia in particular has been pressing for an agreement for the past two years in order to clarify the status of Overseas Chinese before proceeding with the country's first elections", "token_count": 129, "token_end_0based": 128, "token_start_0based": 0, "token_text": "southeast asia 5 chinese-indonesian agreement on dual nationality reached china and indonesia had reached agreement on the renunciation of chinese nationality by those overseas chinese in indonesia who wished to adopt indonesian citizenship a joint declaration of principles is likely to be issued in the next day or two the status of overseas chinese who do not desire indonesian citizenship will be dealt with in subsequent negotiations comment china's past insistence on the principle of dual nationality has been a major irritant to southeast asian countries and the abandonment of this principle will be viewed favorably by these countries indonesia in particular has been pressing for an agreement for the past two years in order to clarify the status of overseas chinese before proceeding with the country's first elections", "unred_source_page": 6}
